<section class="bg-white section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brand-red mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is mobile pizza catering?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Mobile pizza catering brings our wood-fired pizza oven directly to your event location. We set up on-site and prepare fresh, authentic Neapolitan-style pizzas made to order for you and your guests.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">How does Bello Pizza work?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We arrive at your location with our mobile pizza oven, set up our station, and begin preparing fresh pizzas throughout your event. Our team handles all the cooking and service, allowing you to enjoy your event worry-free.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Is the Bello Pizza menu customizable?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Yes! We offer customizable menu options including various pizza styles, toppings, salads, meatballs, pasta, and wings. We can accommodate dietary restrictions and preferences to ensure all your guests are satisfied.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is the typical catering experience timeline?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We typically arrive 1-2 hours before your event to set up and preheat the oven. Service begins at your requested time and continues throughout your event. Most events last 2-4 hours, and we handle all cleanup afterward.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is your minimum order requirement?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We require a minimum of 20 guests for mobile catering events. This ensures we can provide the best service and value for both our team and your event.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">How far in advance should I book?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We recommend booking 2-4 weeks in advance, especially for weekend events and peak seasons. However, we can sometimes accommodate shorter notice depending on availability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What do you need from the venue?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We need a flat surface for our mobile oven (approximately 10x15 feet), access to a standard electrical outlet, and reasonable access for our vehicle. We handle everything else including tables, serving equipment, and cleanup.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
    
    faqItems.forEach(item => {
      const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');
      const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
      const icon = item.querySelector('.faq-icon');
      
      question?.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const isOpen = !answer?.classList.contains('hidden');
        
        // Close all other FAQ items
        faqItems.forEach(otherItem => {
          const otherAnswer = otherItem.querySelector('.faq-answer');
          const otherIcon = otherItem.querySelector('.faq-icon');
          otherAnswer?.classList.add('hidden');
          if (otherIcon) otherIcon.textContent = '+';
          otherIcon?.classList.remove('rotate-45');
        });
        
        // Toggle current item
        if (isOpen) {
          answer?.classList.add('hidden');
          if (icon) icon.textContent = '+';
          icon?.classList.remove('rotate-45');
        } else {
          answer?.classList.remove('hidden');
          if (icon) icon.textContent = 'Ã—';
          icon?.classList.add('rotate-45');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>